        <Parent_String>hydroplanes [300232677], planing vessels [300232903], surface craft [300232901], watercraft by displacement [300232900], watercraft by operating environment [300232899], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
